    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Class Mod</p><p>Prerequisite: Level 11+, At least 1 Uchiha clan Feat, Witnesses one of its loved ones was killed in front of them</p><p>You have experienced true turmoil and trauma, but due to your raw emotion this Mangekyō Sharingan is often called Imperfect. You gain the following benefits:</p><p>• Once per Full-Rest, you can spend a Full-Turn Action to Activate your Imperfect Mangekyō Sharingan. When you do, your Sharingan has twists and transforms into a unique design specific to you. You can maintain your Mangekyō Sharingan in this state for no more than 10 minutes.</p><p>• While in Imperfect Mangekyō Sharingan you gain 5 Mangekyō Art Charges. You can spend these charges to cast a Mangekyō Arts.</p><p>• You gain 2 Mangekyō Arts.</p>",
